### **4. 32_RealTimePlotPanel**  
**Description:**  
Creates live-updating line plots for streaming numeric data using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimePlotPanel - Live Data Visualizer

RealTimePlotPanel is ideal for tracking sensor inputs, API results, or simulation values on a real-time graph.

## Features
- Live updating chart  
- Scrollable plot view  
- Minimal resource usage  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_RealTimePlotPanel.git
cd 32_RealTimePlotPanel
python visualize.py
